## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Tool |
|---|---|
| **Food Detection + NIA Chat** | Gemini 1.5 Flash (vision) + Gemini 1.5 Pro (chat) |
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python) |
| **Database + Auth** | Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage) |
| **Frontend** | React + Vite + TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui |
| **Deployment** | Render.com (backend) + Vercel (frontend) |

---

## 🗄️ Database Schema

```
UserProfile       → id, name, email, age, weight_kg, height_cm,
                    health_issues[], allergies[], daily_calorie_target, created_at

MealLogs          → id, user_id, meal_photo_url, detected_items (jsonb),
                    total_calories, meal_time, meal_type, gemini_insights

DailyTracking     → id, user_id, date, total_calories_consumed,
                    calorie_surplus_or_deficit, junk_score, behaviour_summary, weekly_avg
```

