## ⚠️ Key Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Gemini rate limits (free = 15 RPM) | Cache repeated detections; M4 tests with real limits in Week 3 |
| Gemini misidentifies Indian foods | Piyush's few-shot prompt (Week 2) + M1's 20-food test report |
| Piyush unavailable mid-week | M1 unblocks self using Piyush's Colab notebooks + prompts folder |
| Frontend blocked waiting for APIs | M3 delivers JSON mock fixtures by end of Week 1 |
| Scope creep | Feature freeze after Week 2; extras go to post-MVP backlog |

